[src:pulumi/pulumi] Pulumi was founded in 2017 by former Microsoft employees Joe Duffy and Eric Rudder.
[src:pulumi/pulumi] The open-source Pulumi CLI and SDKs allows users to manage cloud infrastructure resources in Cloud Providers such as AWS, Azure, Google Cloud, and Kubernetes. using programming languages such as Go, JavaScript, TypeScript, Python, Java, C# and YAML.
